Let $R$ be a local Pr\"ufer ring and let $x$ be a regular element of $R$. Then $xR$ is comparable with every principal ideal of $R$.
\end{lemma}



\begin{proof}
The proof follows immediately from \cite[Lemma 3.8]{AJK}.
\end{proof}



